<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
              ColumnWidth="400" FontSize="30" FontFamily="宋体"
              Foreground="Black">
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="36">定义：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">如果数a能被数b整除，b就叫做a的约数。 一个数约数的个数是有限的，最小的约数是1，最大的约数是它本身。</Run>
        <LineBreak />
    </Paragraph>

    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="36">举例：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">在下面分数</Run>
        <Run FontSize="36" FontWeight="Bold" Foreground="Red">4</Run>
        <Run FontSize="30">整除的数。</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28">4, 6, 12, 18, 20, 25, 26, 28, 36, 42, 52, 60, 72, 80, 94, 100</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30" Foreground="Black">答案：</Run>
        <Run FontSize="28" Foreground="LightGray">4, 12, 20, 28, 36, 52, 60, 72, 80, 100</Run>
    </Paragraph>
</FlowDocument>
